81, 326.8929, 327.3625, 327.8812, 327.0872, 326.7998, 327.379, 327.1462, 326.4128, 327.3178, 325.5207, 324.9922, 324.9796, 325.0169, 325.5222, 325.8561, 324.7304, 324.9716, 325.7328, 325.1928, 325.0138, 324.8807, 325.5123, 325.3089, 324.5094, 324.027, 323.8404, 324.2648, 324.3535, 325.172, 325.8153, 326.4166, 326.9599, 328.093, 327.3314, 327.3143, 328.3413, 327.0782, 326.9063, 326.1965, 325.9124, 326.6741, 325.8289, 325.2505, 325.4683, 326.9712, 324.6964, 325.2582, 324.7373, 324.9221, 325.3641, 325.9921, 326.5988, 326.5339, 327.2866, 327.8624, 328.7177, 329.4894, 330.1265, 329.422, 329.1398, 328.6515, 328.2702, 327.446, 327.4075, 327.7545, 327.9944, 326.9871, 326.4865, 326.868, 326.4008, 327.1925, 327.0913, 326.5467, 326.328, 327.3737, 326.9346, 326.7381, 326.8894, 325.6991, 324.4957, 324.9607, 324.9198, 324.0959, 323.5081, 324.4495, 325.2992, 324.8476, 324.4163, 325.2023, 325.2767, 325.728, 325.5262, 324.9538, 323.6728, 323.6129, 323.263, 322.9094, 323.215, 323.3697, 322.5142, 323.9113, 323.3633, 323.5205, 323.2918, 323.8012, 323.8445, 323.8882, 323.9616, 323.9343, 325.2895, 325.676, 325.259, 325.7991, 325.6673, 324.6149, 324.5748, 326.0604, 326.0386, 325.7063, 326.6949, 327.4762, 325.6271, 324.593, 323.0011, 322.8532, 323.0675, 321.3324, 321.369, 321.8671, 322.1149, 321.8372, 321.9617, 321.7544, 321.5244, 320.8714, 321.3417, 321.1227, 321.4047, 321.7834, 322.8054, 321.585, 321.2903, 321.4991, 321.7533, 322.2508, 321.5103, 322.8133, 322.0703, 322.2535, 323.3909, 323.3014, 324.4892, 324.299, 325.6944, 324.3383, 324.6675, 324.4059, 323.7853, 322.6598, 323.8423, 323.0147, 322.936, 323.4326, 324.3886, 324.3473, 323.773, 324.1242, 323.8589, 324.3022, 324.6258, 324.0663, 323.7145, 323.7381, 324.2667, 325.0938, 326.6811, 325.6557, 326.3481, 326.4185, 329.2784, 328.0835, 329.5063, 330.1845, 330.406, 330.0256, 329.3386, 328.9977, 331.592, 331.5813, 329.9962, 328.7754, 328.2263, 329.1642, 328.7746, 328.695, 328.9508, 328.5191, 329.0536, 329.3548, 330.1632, 329.1625, 330.0914, 330.2976, 329.9222, 329.0383, 328.1894, 328.2874, 327.1031, 327.1629, 328.5128, 328.7898, 328.5082, 328.5977, 328.736, 328.9722, 329.8263, 330.0745, 329.1845, 329.9386, 330.9118, 331.4667, 332.3866, 332.1904, 331.6766, 331.7422, 331.9248, 331.7614, 332.6691, 332.3134, 332.878, 331.4187, 332.4657, 332.134], "summary_html": "<h1>库存水平时序偏离度因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 2.21)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本因子利用商品期货多头库存（inventory_lp）的时序偏离度构建截面多空信号。核心逻辑是：当某品种的库存水平显著偏离其历史均值（以滚动Z-score衡量），市场对该品种的供需定价可能存在偏差。因子在截面上对所有品种的Z-score进行百分位排名，做多库存异常偏高的品种、做空库存异常偏低的品种。</p>\n<p>该因子表现极为稳健：样本内Sharpe 2.21，两个半样本分别为2.79和2.54，时序IC正向品种占比86%，与现有因子库最大相关仅0.40，是一个独立且强劲的基本面截面因子。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>2.13</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>8.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-3.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.12</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2516</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>2.26</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.53</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>2.35 / 2.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.43</span></td><td>0.99</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.42</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.1</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.57</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.8</span></td><td>1.14</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.11</span></td><td>1.39</td><td>0.91</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.26</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>56</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2518</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>97.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>44.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{inventory\\_lp}_{i,t} - \\mu_{i}(W)}{\\sigma_{i}(W)}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\mu_{i}(W)</span> 和 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{i}(W)</span> 分别为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 的 <span class=\"math-tex\">W</span> 日滚动均值和标准差。</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t} = \\text{percentile\\_rank}_{cs}(z_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = (\\text{rank}_{i,t} - 0.5) \\times 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{direction}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{signal}_{i,t}}{\\sum_j |\\text{signal}_{j,t}|}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{direction}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\text{vol\\_target}}{\\hat{\\sigma}^{\\text{realized}}_{i,t} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 2.00)</strong>：初始实现，覆盖基准逻辑（inventory_lp zscore -&gt; rank -&gt; continuous signal -&gt; L1 normalize -&gt; vol_target_scale）。参数网格覆盖 zs_window={126,180,252,504}、hold_days={1,5,10,20}、vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20}，以及 inventory_sp 和 lp+sp 组合变体。意外发现 zs=126（半年窗口）优于基准的 zs=252，inv_lp_zs126_h5_raw 达到 Sharpe 2.00。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 1.94)</strong>：扩展参数空间（加入 zs=63/90），添加 sym_rolling_ic_gate 过滤弱品种，测试 inventory_ln 字段。R2 最优变体 inv_combo_zs126_h5_raw (Sharpe 1.94) 略低于 R1，但验证了信号在不同库存字段间的稳健性。IC-gate 变体与非 gate 变体持平，说明信号在大多数品种上均有效（77% 品种 IC&gt;0）。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 2.21)</strong>：关键突破。在 zs=100/126/150 范围内做细粒度参数网格，同时覆盖 vol_target={0.10,0.15,0.20} 和 hold_days={1,5}。发现低 vol_target (0.10) 配合 hold=1 显著提升 Sharpe（从 2.00 到 2.21），原因是更保守的波动率目标降低了噪声品种的仓位暴露。新增 inventory_sn (Sharpe 1.64) 和 inventory_21 (Sharpe -0.41) 的对比确认了 inventory_lp 是最佳字段。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>主要字段</strong>: inventory_lp（多头库存，非空率约36%总体，近年&gt;90%）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（56个有库存数据）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每日换仓或5日再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 基本面数据（inventory_lp）存在历史NaN，早期品种覆盖率较低\n<p>- 低 vol_target (0.10) 导致绝对收益偏低（年化 4.5%），但风险调整后表现优异 - inventory_21 字段信号为负，不适合此逻辑</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 1.89s</li>\n</ul>"}